text:
The food is value for money. While it may not be the tastiest, but for the price you’re paying it is tasty and the portion sizes are generous.

On top of that, they will only cook your food when you order, so that you’ll always receive hot food.

The Saba fish is the most value for money!
Oki. Not bad Saba fish from this stall. Very cool coffeeshop hidden from the rest of the world.
